caption.p: UPLC-QTOF-MS chromatogram of putatively identified compounds from ethyl acetate fraction of H. tuberosus . RT at 1.04 min: fructosylnystose, 1.91 min: chlorogenic acid, 4.06 min: dicaffeoylquinic acid isomer1, 4.41 min: dicaffeoylquinic acid isomer2, 7.11 and 7.60 min: unknown, 8.03 min: pinellic acid.
